Process clustering results into evaluation metrics, rentention, singleton retention, fraction, singleton fraction

Clustering performance of Anchor Clustering(Pre,Post) on pairwise diseases (each with 100K)

result1<-read.csv("clustering_large.csv") 
df_long<- melt(result1, id.vars =c("size","disease","method"), measure.vars = c("single_retention","none_singleton_retention","single_fraction","none_singleton_fraction"))
colnames(df_long)[which(names(df_long) == "variable")] <- "Evaluation matrix"
df_long$Method<-df_long$method


disease.labs <- c("COVID-19 vs. CLL", "HB vs. COVID-19","HB vs. CLL","HB vs. SLE", "SLE vs. COVID-19","SLE vs. CLL")
names(disease.labs) <- c("covidle","HBcovid","HBle","HBsy","sycovid","syle")

df_long2<-df_long[df_long$size=="100k",]

df_long2$`Evaluation matrix`<-gsub("single_retention","singleton retention", df_long2$`Evaluation matrix`)
df_long2$`Evaluation matrix`<-gsub("single_fraction","singleton fraction", df_long2$`Evaluation matrix`)
df_long2$`Evaluation matrix`<-gsub("none_singleton_retention","non-singleton retention", df_long2$`Evaluation matrix`)
df_long2$`Evaluation matrix`<-gsub("none_singleton_fraction","non-singleton fraction", df_long2$`Evaluation matrix`)
df_long2$Method<-gsub("AnchorClusteringPre-VJ","Anchor Clustering Pre-VJ", df_long2$Method)
df_long2$Method<-gsub("AnchorClusteringPost-VJ","Anchor Clustering Post-VJ", df_long2$Method)

df_long2 %>% mutate(size=factor(`Evaluation matrix`)) %>% 
ggplot(aes(x=`Evaluation matrix`, y=value, color=`Evaluation matrix`,shape=Method)) + labs(x = "")+
  geom_segment(aes(x=`Evaluation matrix`, xend=`Evaluation matrix`, y=0, yend=value)) +scale_shape_manual(values=c(19, 13)) +
  geom_point(size=4) + facet_wrap(~disease, labeller = labeller(disease = disease.labs), ncol=6, strip.position = "bottom")+
  theme(strip.background = element_blank(),
    panel.grid.major.x = element_blank(),
    panel.grid.major = element_blank()) +  theme_light()+
  theme(axis.text.x=element_blank(), axis.ticks.x = element_blank(), panel.grid.major = element_blank(),
    panel.grid.minor = element_blank())+ theme(strip.background =element_rect(fill="white"),panel.border = element_blank())+
  theme(strip.text = element_text(colour = 'black'))+
   theme(axis.text = element_text(face = "bold"),
        legend.text = element_text(face = "bold"),
        legend.title = element_text(face = "bold"),
        axis.title = element_text(face = "bold"),
        strip.text = element_text(face = "bold")) +
  xlab("") +
  ylab("Each disease size: 100K ")

eoffice::topptx(filename = "100k.pptx",width = 12, height=4)
